  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><math><mo>(</mo><mi>c</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>)</mo><mo>(</mo><mn>4</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>\u2212</mo><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><mi>c</mi><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>\u2212</mo><mn>10</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mo>(</mo><mn>5</mn><mi>c</mi><mo>\u2212</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>d</mi><mo>)</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>10</mn></math></p>\n<p>The equation above is true for all <em>x</em>, where <em>c</em> and <em>d</em> are constants. What is the value of <em>cd</em>?</p>",
